<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/125313.The_Geography_of_Nowhere"><img alt="The Geography of Nowhere: The Rise and Decline of America&#39;s Man-Made Landscape" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348814708l/125313._SX98_.jpg" />
